I don't have any memory of previous conversations. Each time we start a new conversation, I don't have access to any code or information from past interactions.

If you'd like me to work with some code, you can:
1. Paste the code directly in this conversation
2. Ask me to help you write new code
3. Point me to a file in the project (if there is one)

Is there some code you'd like to work with now?
